================================================================================
3. CACHED PROVIDER LLM RESPONSES (cache/provider/*.json)
================================================================================

Cached responses from external commercial LLM providers (DeepSeek, Together AI)
under `cache/provider/*.json` are **NOT** released under MIT or CC-BY-4.0.

POLICY:

    Cached LLM responses are included in this artifact for academic
    review-time reproducibility, subject to the original providers' terms
    of service.

    They are NOT licensed for:
      - commercial redistribution;
      - use as training data, fine-tuning data, or distillation data for
        any model (whether competing or otherwise);
      - any use prohibited by the upstream provider's then-current ToS.

    Public redistribution outside review-time reproducibility (e.g.,
    camera-ready public release on a content-distribution network) will be
    re-verified against each provider's then-current terms of service
    before distribution.

    Each cached payload preserves the upstream `model` field so that
    attribution to the original provider remains traceable.

PROVIDERS (as of 2026-04, dates of cache collection):

    - DeepSeek API: deepseek-chat, deepseek-reasoner
    - Together AI:  Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-Turbo,
                    meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct-Turbo

